   "body" : "In #15643 the [`github-merge.py`](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/contrib/devtools/github-merge.py) script was updated so that merge commits would include review comments. \r\n\r\nHowever, the script seems to be missing comments. i.e the recently merged #15557 includes:\r\n\r\n```\r\nACKs for commit 184f87:\r\n      jnewbery:\r\n        utACK 184f8785f710d58d9ef82e611591c9cbff5ab89d\r\n    \r\n    Tree-SHA512: fb6542bdfb2c6010e328ec475cf9dcbff4eb2b1a1b27f78010214534908987a5635797196fa05edddffcbcf2987335872dc644a99261886d5cbb34a8f262ad3e\r\n```\r\n\r\nLooking at the PR there should also be `utACKs` from [ryanofsky](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/15557#pullrequestreview-225616510) and [promag](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/15557#issuecomment-482985563).",
